Description: Fragment of strap handle of small pottery amphora or other closed vase; slight traces of white slip; black paint around root. Dull brown micaceous clay. Incised inscription.

Johnston 2006b / The Delta: From Gamma to Zeta (p.28 Table 1)
Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GD.2236)
